    public class CourseSession
extends java.lang.Object

      • scheduleStudySessions

        public boolean scheduleStudySessions()
        Deletes old study sessions that are associated to this course session and calls scheduler to reschedule the amount of hours necessary for this application. This method is used when Users move the CourseSession with studySessions already scheduled
        Returns:
        true if all study sessions are scheduled and false if not all could be scheduled
